# typescript-playground

## Steps

Set up

```
$ npm init -y # initialize npm with defaults
$ npm install -D typescript @types/node # install types
$ npx tsc --init
```
ℹ️ Build into ./build folder

Source

```
$ mkdir src
```

Run
```
$ node build
```

### Tests

```
$ mkdir tests
$ npm install ts-jest --save-dev
$ npm install @types/jest --save-dev

```